  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are about 22m² and are furnished in an elegant Italian style with views across the Mediterranean gardens. The rooms sleep up to three adults with a double or twin beds. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe, bath or shower and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms with Balcony</strong> are approximately 22m² and have either side sea views or garden views.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Sea View Rooms </strong>all have balconies with sea views. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Sea View Rooms </strong>are lovely and spacious with a bedroom and a seating area. A furnished balcony has incredible views along Taormina's coast and Mount Etna. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Classic Room for Single Use </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
